description: AMAZING LOCATION WITH ELEVATOR & 2 HEATED GARAGE PARKING SPOTS! Modern luxury meets classic charm in this stunning two-bedroom, two-bathroom home in the heart of South Boston. Ground up new construction in 2012, this centrally located home is steps to the Broadway Street shops, all bus lines, and SB beaches. Only minutes to the Seaport or downtown Boston, with easy airport and highway access. Chef's kitchen leads to open living/dining area with electric fireplace. Glass slider provides access to private deck with gas line for grilling. Primary bedroom suite easily fits king bed, has a large custom-built closet, and an ensuite bath with glass and marble shower. Second bedroom will also accommodate king-size bed and has ample closet space with direct access to second full bathroom. Other features include custom crown molding, wainscoting, hardwood floors throughout, central air, in-unit laundry, professionally managed building.
